text:
The Ukrainian government gives the success of workers as their own instead of implementing real steps
01 Nov 2019, 16:45 by Maxim Goldarb

In 2018, zarobitchites transferred about $ 11 billion to Ukraine. This year, 12 billion (10% of GDP) is expected. The “green” government will report on the help of the Zarobitchan money about the “successes” and “growth” of the economy.

This is written by Maxim Goldarb on his page on Facebook.
Instead of all possible ways, somehow:

tax cuts for domestic business;
its targeted cheap lending by domestic banks;
protection of domestic producers from the expansion of imports;
credit and tax grace periods when starting a business;
a complete ban on law enforcement intervention in business activities;
revision of quotas with the EU to equalize import-export and equal opportunities for our entrepreneurs;
an increase in social payments and indexation to return the solvency of people lost during Poroshenko, which will entail a surge in consumption in the domestic market;

Power does not and does not even try anything similar, but simply states digital facts and draws unnecessary graphics. Ukrainians continue to leave, Ukraine is aging and depopulated, becoming a convenient, cleared of unnecessary population bridgehead for the expansion of foreign technological capital.
So in the 21st century, under specially created conditions, with the complicity of local authorities, and not war, the territories and national wealth of our state are captured.

Maxim Goldarb


